               <msContents>
                  <summary>Alkimos asks Zenon to return the slaves according to their agreement, as he had now begun work.  Zenon must decide how much should be given as clothing allowance, having regard to his circumstances.  If Zenon refuses his requests, it will do more harm to suffered, they ask for an immediate loan to enable them to carry on.</summary>
